the distilled layer ("what did we decide about X" with a canonical page as
truth), scored for hit-rank across the three pull surfaces (sessions
search, qmd hybrid, paper index). Benchmark prompts live OUTSIDE indexed
Brain roots (qmd spike caveat). Baseline now, rerun as the corpus grows —
recall quality measured, not vibed. Page-quality benching stays on the
observational-memory map.
